-- Prokhorov’s Onexim Confirms Talks on Polyus Gold Sale
-- B y   S t e p h e n   B i e r m a n
-- 2012-09-12T04:53:57Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-09-12/prokhorov-s-onexim-confirms-talks-on-polyus-gold-sale.html
Russian billionaire  Mikhail Prokhorov ’s Onexim Holdings Ltd. confirmed that it’s in talks
with two potential buyers for some or all of its 37.78 percent
stake in Polyus Gold International Ltd., according to an e-
mailed statement from Onexim.  Onexim is discussing selling stakes of less than 20
percent to each of the two buyers, according to the statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
